features:
• Support WSL 2 projects using WSL interpreter
  • Fixed: Find Usages does not prompt when method overrides/implements base method
  • Fixed: Can't validate PHP XDebug >= 2.9 configuration

Many other features and changes from the IntelliJ platform and web are also included.
